#. Tag: title
#: details-schedules.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid "Schedules"
msgstr "Časovni plani"

#. Tag: title
#: details-schedules.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Schedules maintain information about transactions that occur one or more "
"times over a specified period of time."
msgstr ""
"Časovni plani hranijo informacije o transakcijah, ki se zgodijo enkrat ali "
"večkrat v določenem časovnem obdobju."

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sometimes called a scheduled transaction or a recurring transaction, a "
"schedule provides a means to record information about a transaction that "
"happens on a regular basis. You can schedule deposit, transfer, withdrawal, "
"and loan transactions. There is a lot of flexibility in schedules, including "
"transactions that occur Once, or on a basis of number of Days, Weeks, Half-"
"months, Months, or Years."
msgstr ""
"Razpored, ki se včasih imenuje načrtovana transakcija ali ponavljajoča se "
"transakcija, ponuja način za beleženje informacij o transakciji, ki se redno "
"izvaja. Načrtujete lahko transakcije depozitov, prenosov, dvigov in posojil. "
"Razporedi so zelo prilagodljivi, vključno s transakcijami, ki se zgodijo "
"enkrat ali na podlagi števila dni, tednov, pol-mesecev, mesecev ali let."

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Because you know these transactions happen regularly, whether they are "
"payments made to you or payments you make to someone else, you can create a "
"Schedule to record information about the recurring details to simplify and "
"easily remember when the event will next occur."
msgstr ""
"Ker veste, da se te transakcije izvajajo redno, ne glede na to, ali gre za "
"plačila vam ali plačila, ki jih opravite nekomu drugemu, lahko ustvarite "
"časovni plan za beleženje informacij o ponavljajočih se podrobnostih, da "
"poenostavite in si preprosto zapomnite, kdaj se bo dogodek naslednjič zgodil."

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Schedules can be created to reflect money coming in or out of your accounts "
"on a consistent basis. Common uses include paychecks, taxes, insurance, "
"credit card payments, dues, interest, loans, mortgage, and rents. Scheduling "
"a payment like these provides for a useful reminder so you can manage "
"expected future financial matters effectively."
msgstr ""
"Časovne plane je mogoče ustvariti tako, da dosledno prikazujejo denar, ki "
"prihaja na vaše račune ali iz njih. Pogoste uporabe vključujejo plače, "
"davke, zavarovanje, plačila s kreditnimi karticami, dajatve, obresti, "
"posojila, hipoteko in najemnine. Načrtovanje takšnega plačila je koristen "
"opomnik, da lahko učinkovito upravljate pričakovane prihodnje finančne "
"zadeve."

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A schedule consists of two main parts: the transaction data and the "
"scheduling data. The scheduling data records the occurrence of the schedule, "
"&ie;, when the transaction is to be entered into the ledger and how. The "
"transaction data records the normal details about the transaction, including "
"options for Payment method, Account, Pay to/from, Category, Tags, Memo, Due "
"date, Amount, and Status. Along with these, you can also select additional "
"options based on when to process the transaction."
msgstr ""
"Časovni plan je sestavljen iz dveh glavnih delov: podatkov o transakcijah in "
"podatkov o razporejanju. Podatki o razporejanju beležijo pojav razporeda, "
"&ie; kdaj je treba transakcijo vnesti v glavno knjigo in kako. Podatki o "
"transakciji beležijo običajne podrobnosti o transakciji, vključno z "
"možnostmi za način plačila, račun, plačilo za/od, kategorijo, značke, "
"opombo, datum zapadlosti, znesek in status. Poleg teh lahko izberete tudi "
"dodatne možnosti glede na to, kdaj želite obdelati transakcijo."

#. Tag: title
#: details-schedules.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Types of schedules"
msgstr "Vrste časovnih planov"

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are four different types of schedules in &kmymoney;:"
msgstr "V &kmymoney; obstajajo štiri različne vrste časovnih planov:"

#. Tag: title
#: details-schedules.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deposits"
msgstr "Depoziti"

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These schedules are for money coming into your account, such as a paycheck, "
"bonus, or interest income."
msgstr ""
"Ti časovni razporedi so za denar, ki prihaja na vaš račun, kot je plača, "
"bonus ali prihodek od obresti."

#. Tag: title
#: details-schedules.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bills/Withdrawals"
msgstr "Računi/Dvigi"

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These are for money going out of your account, such as a membership, utility "
"bill, tax payment, or car registration."
msgstr ""
"Ti so za denar, ki gre z vašega računa, kot je članstvo, račun za komunalo, "
"plačilo davka ali registracijo avtomobila."

#. Tag: title
#: details-schedules.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transfer"
msgstr "Prenos"

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These are for money going out of one account and into another account, such "
"as making a credit card payment from your checking account."
msgstr ""
"Ti so za denar, ki gre z enega računa na drug račun, kot je plačilo s "
"kreditno kartico z vašega transakcijskega računa."

#. Tag: title
#: details-schedules.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "Loans"
msgstr "Posojila"

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These are a special type of schedule, which is created when you create a "
"<link linkend=\"details.loans\">Loan account</link>."
msgstr ""
"To je posebna vrsta časovnega razporeda, ki se ustvari, ko ustvarite <link "
"linkend=\"details.loans\">račun za posojilo</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-schedules.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Schedules View"
msgstr "Pogled časovnih planov"

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the Schedules View by clicking the <guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"schedule_view.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> Scheduled transactions icon in "
"the view selector."
msgstr ""
"Odprite pogled časovnih razporedov tako, da kliknete <guiicon> "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"schedule_view.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> ikono "
"načrtovanih transakcij v pogledu selektor."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-schedules.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>schedules view</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>pogled časovnih razporedov</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-schedules.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>schedules view</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>pogled časovnih razporedov</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Schedules View consists of a single display area with a <guibutton>New "
"Schedule...</guibutton> button and a <guilabel>Filter</guilabel> text box "
"above it."
msgstr ""
"Pogled časovnih razporedov je sestavljen iz enega samega območja prikaza z "
"gumbom <guibutton>Nov časovni plan...</guibutton> in besedilnim poljem "
"<guilabel>Filter</guilabel> nad njim."

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a new schedule click <guibutton>New Schedule...</guibutton>. "
"&kmymoney; will display the new schedule dialog, which can be used to create "
"a Deposit, Transfer, or Bill/Withdrawal schedule. Loan schedules are handled "
"differently, as described in the <link linkend=\"details.loans\">Loans</"
"link> section of this manual."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti nov časovni razpored, kliknite <guibutton>Nov razpored..."
"</guibutton>. &kmymoney; bo prikazalo novo pogovorno okno časovnega plana, "
"ki ga lahko uporabite za ustvarjanje razporeda pologov, prenosov ali računov/"
"dvigov. Razporedi posojil se obravnavajo drugače, kot je opisano v razdelku "
"<link linkend=\"details.loans\">Posojila</link> tega priročnika."

#. Tag: title
#: details-schedules.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid "The New Schedule dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno Nov časovni plan"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-schedules.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>new schedule dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>pogovorno okno nov časovni plan</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-schedules.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>new schedule dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>pogovorno okno nov časovni plan</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A New Schedule dialog is now shown, prompting for the schedule and "
"transaction details. The requested data include the following:"
msgstr ""
"Zdaj je prikazano pogovorno okno Nov časovni plan, ki zahteva časovni plan "
"in podrobnosti transakcije. Zahtevani podatki vključujejo naslednje:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "Schedule Name"
msgstr "Ime časovnega plana"

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "Next due date"
msgstr "Naslednji rok"

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequency"
msgstr "Pogostost"

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "Payment method"
msgstr "Način plačila"

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "Amount"
msgstr "Znesek"

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other transaction details"
msgstr "Druge podrobnosti transakcije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "Schedule options"
msgstr "Možnosti časovnega plana"

#. Tag: title
#: details-schedules.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filling in the Schedule name, Frequency, and Payment information."
msgstr "Izpolnjevanje podatkov o imenu časovnega plana, pogostosti in plačilu."

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the name of the schedule and the date of the next occurrence into "
"their respective fields. The name is how the schedule will be labelled in "
"the Schedules View and other displays. Specify how often the schedule should "
"occur, using the Frequency field and dropdown list. If the dropdown is set "
"to <quote>Once</quote>, the Frequency field will be disabled. Otherwise, the "
"dropdown indicates a time interval, and the transaction will happen every "
"<emphasis>Frequency</emphasis> occurrences of that interval. Note that some "
"intervals can be indicated in more than one way, such as 6 x \"weekly\" or 3 "
"x \"every other week\" or 2 x \"every three weeks.\" You cannot indicate "
"fractions of an interval, such as twice per month; you need to use a shorter "
"interval, such as 1 x \"every half month.\""
msgstr ""
"V ustrezna polja vnesite ime časovnega plana in datum naslednjega pojava. "
"Ime je, kako bo časovni plan označen v Pogledu planov in na drugih zaslonih. "
"S poljem Frekvenca in spustnim seznamom določite, kako pogosto naj se izvaja "
"časovni plan. Če je spustni meni nastavljen na <quote>Enkrat</quote>, bo "
"polje Frekvenca onemogočeno. Sicer spustni meni označuje časovni interval in "
"transakcija se bo zgodila ob vsaki <emphasis>Frekvenci</emphasis> pojava "
"tega intervala. Upoštevajte, da so nekateri intervali lahko označeni na več "
"kot en način, na primer 6 x \"tedensko\" ali 3 x \"vsak drugi teden\" ali 2 "
"x \"vsake tri tedne.\" Ne morete označiti delov intervala, na primer dvakrat "
"na mesec; morate uporabiti krajši interval, na primer 1 x \"vsakega pol "
"meseca.\""

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the amount varies transaction to transaction make sure to check the "
"<guilabel>The amount is an estimate because it varies for each payment</"
"guilabel> checkbox in the <guilabel>Options</guilabel> area below, and you "
"will be prompted for the correct amount when it is entered into the ledger. "
"The amount is entered as a positive number in either the <guilabel>Payment</"
"guilabel> or <guilabel>Deposit</guilabel> field. The other required fields "
"in this area are the Account and the Category. The <guilabel>Status</"
"guilabel> dropdown indicates the state of the transaction when &kmymoney; "
"enters it into the ledger. The remaining fields in this section are optional."
msgstr ""
"Če se znesek razlikuje od transakcije do transakcije, preverite potrditveno "
"polje <guilabel>Znesek je ocena, ker se razlikuje za vsako plačilo</"
"guilabel> v spodnjem območju <guilabel>Možnosti</guilabel> in pozvani boste, "
"da vnesete pravi znesek, ko je vpisan v knjigo. Znesek se vnese kot "
"pozitivno število v polje <guilabel>Plačilo</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Polog</"
"guilabel>. Drugi zahtevani polji na tem področju sta račun in kategorija. "
"Spustni meni <guilabel>Status</guilabel> prikazuje stanje transakcije, ko "
"&kmymoney; vpiše v glavno knjigo. Preostala polja v tem razdelku so "
"neobvezna."

#. Tag: title
#: details-schedules.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modifying the Schedule Options section"
msgstr "Spreminjanje razdelka Možnosti časovnega plana"

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>If this schedule occurs on a non-processing date:</guilabel> "
"dropdown allows you to choose how to handle non-processing days. Non-"
"processing days include weekends and holidays known to &kmymoney; for the "
"region specified in the <link linkend=\"details.settings.schedules.calendar"
"\">appropriate configuration option</link>. If the schedule occurs on a non-"
"processing day you can choose whether to <guilabel>Do not change the date</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Change the date to the previous processing day</"
"guilabel>, or <guilabel>Change the date to the next processing day</"
"guilabel>. This option is available to replicate some of the real world "
"business operational processing."
msgstr ""
"Spustni meni <guilabel>Če se ta razpored pojavi na dan, ko ni obdelave:</"
"guilabel> vam omogoča, da izberete, kako ravnati z dnevi, ko ni obdelav. "
"Dnevi brez obdelav vključujejo vikende in praznike, ki jih &kmymoney; za "
"regijo, navedeno v <link linkend=\"details.settings.schedules.calendar"
"\">ustrezni možnosti konfiguracije</link>. Če je razpored na dan brez "
"obdelav, lahko izberete, ali <guilabel>Ne spremeni datuma</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Spremeni datum na prejšnji dan obdelave</guilabel> ali "
"<guilabel>Spremeni datum na naslednji dan obdelave</guilabel>. Ta možnost je "
"na voljo za posnemanje nekaterih poslovnih operativnih procesov v resničnem "
"svetu."

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>The amount is an estimate because is varies for each payment</"
"guilabel> checkbox allows you to select whether &kmymoney; automatically "
"enters that amount into the ledger or prompts you for the actual amount when "
"the schedule is due."
msgstr ""
"Potrditveno polje <guilabel>Znesek je ocena, ker se razlikuje za vsako "
"plačilo</guilabel> omogoča izbiro, ali &kmymoney; samodejno vnese ta znesek "
"v glavno knjigo ali vas pozove k vnosu dejanskega zneska, ko pride rok "
"zapadlosti."

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Do not change amount of category but modify exchange rate of "
"transaction</guilabel> checkbox can be used when the schedule involves an "
"account and a category with different currencies. If it is not selected, the "
"amount specified is used when the transaction is entered into the ledger. "
"Checking the box tells &kmymoney; that the amount is specified in the "
"currency of the category. You will still need to confirm the other value or "
"the conversion rate when the transaction is entered into the ledger."
msgstr ""
"Potrditveno polje <guilabel>Ne spreminjaj zneska kategorije, ampak spremeni "
"menjalni tečaj transakcije</guilabel> je mogoče uporabiti, ko razpored "
"vključuje račun in kategorijo z različnimi valutami. Če ni izbran, se "
"navedeni znesek uporabi, ko se transakcija vnese v knjigo. Ob potrditvi "
"polja &kmymoney; da je znesek naveden v valuti kategorije. Še vedno boste "
"morali potrditi drugo vrednost ali menjalno razmerje, ko bo transakcija "
"vnesena v glavno knjigo."

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Process this schedule always at the last day of the month</"
"guilabel> checkbox allows for scheduling for irregular month-end date "
"processing."
msgstr ""
"Potrditveno polje <guilabel>Obdelaj ta časovni plan vedno na zadnji dan v "
"mesecu</guilabel> omogoča načrtovanje za neredno obdelavo ob koncu meseca."

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Enter this schedule into the register automatically when it is "
"due</guilabel> checkbox tells &kmymoney; to enter the transaction into the "
"ledger on the correct date without human intervention. Otherwise, when the "
"transaction is due to be entered, &kmymoney; will open a dialog box asking "
"you to confirm that you want it to be entered. This behavior is "
"configurable, and more information can be found in the <link linkend="
"\"details.settings.schedules\">Settings</link> section."
msgstr ""
"Potrditveno polje <guilabel>Samodejno vnesi ta razpored v register, ko "
"zapade</guilabel> pove, da &kmymoney; za vnos transakcije v glavno knjigo "
"vstavi pravi datum brez človeškega posredovanja. V nasprotnem primeru, ko je "
"treba transakcijo vnesti, &kmymoney; se bo odprlo pogovorno okno, v katerem "
"boste morali potrditi, da ga želite vnesti. To vedenje je mogoče "
"konfigurirati, več informacij pa najdete v razdelku <link linkend=\"details."
"settings.schedules\">Nastavitve</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you know the schedule will not continue indefinitely, check the "
"<guilabel>This schedule will end at some time</guilabel> and you can enter "
"either the <guilabel>Number of transactions remaining:</guilabel> or the "
"<guilabel>Date of final transaction</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Če veste, da se časovni plan ne bo nadaljeval v nedogled, označite "
"<guilabel>Ta časovni razpored se bo končal ob določenem času</guilabel> in "
"lahko vnesete <guilabel>Število preostalih transakcij:</guilabel> ali "
"<guilabel>Datum končne transakcije</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you have entered all the necessary information click <guibutton>OK</"
"guibutton> to continue."
msgstr ""
"Ko ste vnesli vse potrebne informacije, kliknite <guibutton>V redu</"
"guibutton> za nadaljevanje."

#. Tag: title
#: details-schedules.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing schedules"
msgstr "Urejanje časovnih planov"

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To edit a schedule simply select the entry in the list, then right-click and "
"select <guimenuitem>Edit scheduled transaction</guimenuitem> in the context "
"menu. This will bring up a dialog similar to the <guilabel>New Scheduled "
"transaction</guilabel> dialog, where you can update the necessary data."
msgstr ""
"Če želite urediti časovni plan, preprosto izberite vnos na seznamu, nato z "
"desno miškino tipko kliknite in v kontekstnem meniju izberite "
"<guimenuitem>Uredi načrtovano transakcijo</guimenuitem>. To bo prikazalo "
"pogovorno okno, podobno pogovornemu oknu <guilabel>Nova načrtovana "
"transakcija</guilabel>, kjer lahko posodobite potrebne podatke."

#. Tag: title
#: details-schedules.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deleting schedules"
msgstr "Brisanje časovnih planov"

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To delete a schedule simply select the entry in the list, then right-click "
"and select <guimenuitem>Delete scheduled transaction</guimenuitem>. in the "
"context menu."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrisati časovni plan, preprosto izberite vnos na seznamu, nato z "
"desno miškino tipko kliknite in izberite <guimenuitem>Izbriši načrtovano "
"transakcijo</guimenuitem>. v kontekstnem meniju."

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that while many actions in &kmymoney; can be undone, this is not true "
"for deleting a schedule. If you delete a schedule, and realize you did not "
"want to do that, you will have to completely recreate it from scratch."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da čeprav je veliko dejanj v &kmymoney; mogoče razveljaviti, to "
"ne velja za brisanje časovnega plana. Če izbrišete časovni plan in "
"ugotovite, da tega ne želite storiti, ga boste morali popolnoma znova "
"ustvariti iz nič."

#. Tag: title
#: details-schedules.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid "Duplicating schedules"
msgstr "Podvajanje časovnih planov"

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To duplicate a schedule simply select the entry in the list, then right-"
"click and select <guimenuitem>Duplicate scheduled transaction</guimenuitem> "
"in the context menu."
msgstr ""
"Če želite podvojiti časovni plan, preprosto izberite vnos na seznamu, nato z "
"desno miškino tipko kliknite in v kontekstnem meniju izberite "
"<guimenuitem>Podvoji načrtovano transakcijo</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-schedules.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid "Entering scheduled transactions"
msgstr "Vnos načrtovanih transakcij"

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Entering a scheduled transaction means actually creating a transaction in "
"the appropriate ledger, using the details specified in the schedule. "
"Scheduled transactions can be entered in one of 3 different ways:"
msgstr ""
"Vnos načrtovane transakcije pomeni dejansko ustvarjanje transakcije v "
"ustrezni glavni knjigi z uporabo podrobnosti, navedenih v časovnem planu. "
"Načrtovane transakcije je mogoče vnesti na enega od treh različnih načinov:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Manually, by right-clicking the entry in the Schedules View and selecting "
"<guilabel>Enter next transaction</guilabel> in the context menu."
msgstr ""
"Ročno, z desnim klikom na vnos v Pogledu časovnih planov in izbiro "
"<guilabel>Vnesi naslednjo transakcijo</guilabel> v kontekstnem meniju."

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; can enter them with or without your interaction upon startup."
msgstr "&kmymoney; jih lahko vnese z ali brez vaše interakcije ob zagonu."

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; can enter them with your interaction during online banking or "
"when you import a bank statement."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; jih lahko vnese z vašo interakcijo med spletnim bančništvom ali "
"ko uvozite bančni izpisek."

#. Tag: title
#: details-schedules.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid "Confirming the transaction to enter"
msgstr "Potrjevanje transakcije za vstop"

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first and third methods will display an <guilabel>Enter scheduled "
"transaction</guilabel> dialog (possibly after displaying an informational "
"window about the process.) This dialog prompts you to confirm or update the "
"required information that was entered when you created the schedule."
msgstr ""
"Prva in tretja metoda bosta prikazala pogovorno okno <guilabel>Vnesite "
"načrtovano transakcijo</guilabel> (po možnosti po prikazu okna z "
"informacijami o postopku.) To pogovorno okno vas pozove, da potrdite ali "
"posodobite zahtevane informacije, ki ste jih vnesli, ko ste ustvarili "
"časovni plan ."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-schedules.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid "enter scheduled transaction"
msgstr "vnos načrtovane transakcije"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-schedules.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid "enter schedule transaction"
msgstr "vnos načrtovane transakcije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This information can be changed, and the changes can be applied to just this "
"one instance of the schedule or to all subsequent transactions. After "
"checking that all the data is correct clicking <guibutton>OK</guibutton> "
"will add the transaction to the ledger and update the next due date of the "
"schedule to the next occurrence. If you have changed any of the transaction "
"data a further confirmation of what you changed will be displayed, giving "
"you a final chance to accept or reject the changes."
msgstr ""
"Te informacije je mogoče spremeniti, spremembe pa je mogoče uporabiti samo "
"za ta en primerek časovnega plana ali za vse naslednje transakcije. Ko "
"preverite, ali so vsi podatki pravilni, boste s klikom na <guibutton>V redu</"
"guibutton> dodali transakcijo v glavno knjigo in posodobili naslednji datum "
"zapadlosti razporeda na naslednji dogodek. Če ste spremenili katerega od "
"podatkov o transakciji, bo prikazana nadaljnja potrditev, kaj ste "
"spremenili, kar vam bo dalo zadnjo priložnost, da sprejmete ali zavrnete "
"spremembe."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-schedules.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>confirm manual transaction changes</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>potrdite ročne spremembe transakcij</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-schedules.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>confirm manual transaction changes</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>potrdite sprememb ročnih transakcij</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select what you want to do with the information presented and click "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton> or <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite, kaj želite narediti s predstavljenimi informacijami, in kliknite "
"<guibutton>V redu</guibutton> ali <guibutton>Prekliči</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-schedules.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid "Letting &kmymoney; enter the scheduled transaction(s) for you"
msgstr "Dovolite &kmymoney; vnesite načrtovane transakcije za vas"

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alternatively, &kmymoney; can check which schedules are due upon startup and "
"enter them for you if the appropriate option was checked when setting up the "
"schedule."
msgstr ""
"Druga možnost je &kmymoney; lahko ob zagonu preveri, kateri časovni plani so "
"zapadli, in jih vnese namesto vas, če je bila ob nastavitvi časovnega plana "
"označena ustrezna možnost."

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:347
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the option was not checked then &kmymoney; will open the previously "
"mentioned dialog and you can follow the steps mentioned there. &kmymoney; "
"will also open the dialog if the amount is an estimate so you can enter the "
"actual amount."
msgstr ""
"Če možnost ni označena, bo &kmymoney; odprl prej omenjeno pogovorno okno in "
"lahko sledite tam omenjenim korakom. &kmymoney; bo odprl tudi pogovorno "
"okno, če je znesek ocenjen, tako da lahko vnesete dejanski znesek."

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also opt to have &kmymoney; not check which transactions are "
"scheduled on startup by deselecting the option in the Settings dialog and "
"any overdue transaction or transactions due 'today' will be shown in the "
"Home view for you to enter manually."
msgstr ""
"Lahko se tudi odločite, da imate &kmymoney; ne preverjajte, katere "
"transakcije so načrtovane ob zagonu, tako da počistite izbiro možnosti v "
"pogovornem oknu z nastavitvami, vse zapadle transakcije ali transakcije, ki "
"zapadejo 'danes', pa bodo prikazane v domačem pogledu, ki ga lahko vnesete "
"ročno."

